==Classifications==
{|class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" style="font-size: 85%"
!scope=row colspan="16" style="text-align: center;"|'''Final classification after 15 Special Stages'''
|-
!scope=col style="border-right: 3px solid grey;" |Position
!scope=col|Car<br />Number
!scope=col|Driver
!scope=col|Co-driver
!scope=col|Car
!scope=col|Entrant
!scope=col class="unsortable"|Registration<br />{{nowrap|([[List of international vehicle registration codes|Country]] / [[vehicle registration plate|plate]])}}
